AUDIO: 'If you\'re an AI enthusiast and you interact with chatbots every single day for work, this video is going to be a massive upgrade to your workflow. I\'ll show you how I use a tool called typing mine to build custom AI agents that automate a lot of things for me within a chat interface, which allows me to send'

